          ],
          "returnType": "Promise<HTMLImageElement>",
          "description": "Renders the SVG markup into a fully loaded HTMLImageElement. When options.width or options.height are provided, the values are injected into the root <svg> element before rasterisation so the browser renders at the requested pixel dimensions rather than the intrinsic size. Creates a temporary image/svg+xml object URL, assigns it to an <img> element, and revokes the URL once loading settles. Rejects on load error or abort."
        },
